  "name": "Call And Response",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>Your composition takes the form of a call-and-response chant, which lets your allies continue the effect without you.</p>\n<p>If your next action is to cast a composition cantrip with a duration of 1 round, it becomes a call.</p>\n<p>While the spell is active, one ally affected by the spell can respond to your call as a single action that has the auditory and concentrate traits to extend the spell's duration by 1 round. Only one ally can respond to a given call, and responding to the ally's response has no additional effect.</p>"
